HEADWORD: Contestant
<hw>Con*test"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>contestant</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who contests; an opponent; a
litigant; a disputant; one who claims that which has been awarded to
another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

